==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|permeat|ing}}

# To [[pass]] through the [[pore]]s or [[interstice]]s of; to [[penetrate]] and pass through without causing [[rupture]] or [[displacement]]; -- applied especially to fluids which pass through substances of loose texture; as, water permeates sand.
# To [[enter]] and [[spread]] through; to [[pervade]].

